{
  "id": "RAW_bd63214e",
  "title": "我把这一年的 AI 聊天记录，让 AI 做人生总结后，我破防了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647678286&idx=1&sn=a66a1e8d763eb5445deafd1cc556b0c0",
  "date": "2025-12-26 01:19:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">年末了，很多人都在做年终总结。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">ChatGPT在做，我前几天刚刚测完，我的结果是这样子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500194601\" data-ratio=\"1.0943738656987296\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1102\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9cbc989d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRz4qR0bpjZXs1tQuyMFXczNIK9a03uTHq8icfeovY67j3icKWtopqUUHzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是ChatGPT代表不了我。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为我的AI，用的实在是太杂了，ChatGPT、Gemini、DeepSeek、豆包、GLM等等等等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我突然在想，如果我把我这一年，跟所有AI的聊天记录，都导出出来，扔给AI，那是不是，这就是我这一年，最好的注脚？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用这一年，所有的聊天记录，分析我是一个什么样的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我觉得，这比任何心理测试或者我的记忆，都要准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我的记忆会骗人，会不准，但是有我这一年所有聊天记录的AI，他不会骗人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个想法，在脑子里萦绕，最终还是在夜里1点钟爬起床来，说干就干。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">步骤和思路其实很简单，就两步：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1. 想办法导出ChatGPT、Gemini、豆包、DeepSeek的聊天记录，因为这四个我今年用的最多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2. 把这些聊天记录，一起扔给某一个AI，让他给我分析。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第一步我本来以为特别简单，因为ChatGPT我知道有一个功能，就是导出聊天记录。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194603\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.876577840112202\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"713\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd7f085d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzWI0Lia85EJafntOdR7bfTbnDf8Snzq9V4SjzWd8gjzibkYSMrXW2PpWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我本来没想那么多，就非常简单的，点了确认导出，然后信心满满的等着他给我推送这个聊天记录的下载链接。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">几分钟后，下载链接发送到了我的邮箱里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194604\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4913494809688581\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"867\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c147679&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzZ9ToMUMdCXvNkS0jRz6YG1ZRFSCocuLicjzc89fWxx9KIpceMjrBglQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我点了下载，然后，当我打开文件的那一刻，我直接懵逼了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为，这一份文件，200多M。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我人麻了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194607\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8236559139784946\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"465\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"465\" data-backh=\"383\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb13ca68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRziagsT7JlFvSBx7vV9INicfWibq7YYa2ZiaLDSPj01laLo7ce7V5iaiaSmJPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这玩意大到，我用Trae打开，直接崩了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194608\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46153846153846156\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"481\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"481\" data-backh=\"222\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=653c126c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzoq2oGLanibXDIKSwEz93e7WaruPDjm6W3L106u2spcdibbOWEicACumuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为有一个致命的问题，就是ChatGPT的导出，无法选择时间，所以他把我从2023年开始，到现在，所有的聊天记录全部都导出了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这3年的聊天记录，一共200多M，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2个亿的字符，959万字。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194610\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2888198757763975\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"322\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"322\" data-backh=\"93\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7879382&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzW8eXj44P6YN82pq74FyCcTZkoxQOK2ZBQGedHcIa0usNgJDoNAficdQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我尼玛...</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且这个聊天记录里面，还没有给每一个对话标注时间属性，所以，我想写脚本把2025年的拆出来，甚至都没法拆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194609\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.524074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4fbeb38d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzwonVvJYSKqLj2g5pMTib5pKUibsZUI3M1N4kYvZTeUNKHXnLfgk3nhZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这959万字的文档，什么AI都不可能吃得下去啊。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而导出记录这个事，不仅ChatGPT这遇到了巨大的阻碍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在其他的所有AI产品里，全都遇到了更巨大的问题，就是除了DeepSeek这个好心人之外，其他的，他们连聊天记录导出的这个功能都木有。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，DeepSeek真的是清流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194605\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6747448979591837\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"784\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea14add2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRz7HmhT2QSxvvVZ1xN7AicxBicU3G13Gg7o5ib757wSfO6JicNJ0Ohc3SaDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且里面的聊天记录，是带有时间的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194606\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4898148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b7b2459&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzejpxjQbVrIFxIZspxcwKLvfTw455vxlGHHjXFl1mAujWMwXHEKk1MQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的是清流了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是没用啊，DeepSeek我也就年初用用，但是其实后面，我用的最多的还是ChatGPT、Gemini、豆包这三。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">ChatGPT是我处理所有办公场景、写内容做策划用，Gemini是我写代码用，豆包是手机端懒得上魔法日常简单问题问答用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这几个最重要的东西用不了，只能用DeepSeek的聊天记录，那顶个屁用啊= =</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以只能，想别的路了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一顿搜索之后，我找到了一个感觉很符合我要求的工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也是一个KOL开发的免费插件，叫Chat Memo。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194612\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.981029810298103\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"738\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=196bbda1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzQpCMIID7pRwwsMNicJKWHaDZlLn5CWbibQAIXsJGx8omFPoBzCMQ3dGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">网址在此：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://chatmemo.ai/\" target=\"_blank\">https://chatmemo.ai/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194613\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7004504504504504\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1776\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67bd97a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRz5RyrWwqdxics0yP5ypGyWlrPdWua0tV5LBHfqgB8UUJjH48YrGKiaerg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">作用大概就是通过Chrome的这个插件，把你所有的聊天记录，都备份一份在你的本地，然后随意导出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个备份在本地不上云非常的重要，因为我的聊天记录里，有太多太多敏感信息了，我可不敢把这个东西，随便给别人看。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">目前支持这些AI工具，我的四个都在里面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194614\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1994535519125683\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"732\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf1ff913&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzcHiaE4xw3uJgyWFOWaOLHAp2U8lsVIRNksiafEpIsYaBAuP86wxsCFhQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直接在Chrome商店或者通过安装包安装以后。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你就会发现，他出现在了插件栏里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194616\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6914893617021277\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"376\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"376\" data-backh=\"260\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9b7d3a2b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzEeROjFfrZHbOZ2MqcUXoVbhqjKwBla3Eg4z7GLZbRickDWldO6vKeHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后回到AI应用界面，比如ChatGPT，原地刷新一下，就能看到右边多了这么一个东西，叫自动记忆，可以点开的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194615\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5611111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f6628f3d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpYunJtzX5qTEVYHApg7TRzqfJicp18mibCbEBwILzXmV5jvW15ADasv7icUNrhdhcLiaT0ArPNuSVaPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而使用方法也巨简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是你把你想导出的记忆，在左边的对话栏里，点击一下，他就会自动同步到记忆目录里了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我录了个屏，大家可以简单看一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个做法，有好处，也有坏处。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">好处就是，你只有手动点击以后，这个记录才会进入到</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Chat Memo的记忆模块里，也就是说，你完全可以更精准的挑选，有一些没啥关系的明显就是垃圾信息，就没必要进记忆了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我的这些玩意。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500194621\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3225806451612903\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"899\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a59bc073&amp;u=https%3